OL,3,CStars share sadness as TV studio is
OL,4,Ctorn down to make way for new
OL,5,Cdevelopment
OL,7,FLoose Women star Gloria Hunniford has
OL,8,Fshared her sadness at the demolition
OL,9,Fof an iconic TV studio.
OL,11,FThe London Television Centre has been
OL,12,Fa familiar landmark on the South Bank
OL,13,Ffor more than 50 years.
OL,15,FThe former headquarters of London
OL,16,FWeekend Television occupied a prime
OL,17,Friverside spot between Waterloo and
OL,18,FBlackfriars Bridges.
