OL,7,FDemolition contractors are tearing
OL,8,Fdown the studios and distinctive 19-
OL,9,Fstorey tower before the site is
OL,10,Fredeveloped.
OL,12,FThe studios which opened in 1972 gave
OL,13,Fbirth to some of the nation's
OL,14,Ffavourite shows from Upstairs
OL,15,FDownstairs to Ant & Dec's Saturday
OL,16,FNight Takeaway.
