OL,7,FOther notable productions included
OL,8,FWorld of Sport, On the Buses, Blind
OL,9,FDate, Surprise Surprise, The Dame Edna
OL,10,FExperience, Aspel & Co and Game For A
OL,11,FLaugh.
OL,13,FHunniford, who interviewed Hollywood
OL,14,FStars for her chat show Sunday Sunday,
OL,15,Freturned to the site with ITV News
OL,16,Fwhere she saw demolition work underway.
OL,18,F"I hate looking back at the building
OL,19,Fand seeing it the way it is," Gloria
OL,20,Fsaid.
