OL,7,FShe added: "You can imagine that in
OL,8,FNorthern Ireland I had been dealing
OL,9,Fsince 1969 with bombs, bullets and
OL,10,Fbarricades and to leave that behind
OL,11,Fand come to do a totally different
OL,12,Fkind of programme with all the glamour
OL,13,Fand gloss and the excitement it was a
OL,14,Fhuge thing.
OL,16,F"My dress allowance in the 1980 for
OL,17,Fone programme per week was #1,000."
