OL,7,FActor Matthew Kelly's first job at the
OL,8,Fstudio was to deliver one line in a
OL,9,Fpilot for sitcom, Hold The Fort, in
OL,10,F1979.
OL,12,FIt led to a series and appearances on
OL,13,FPunchlines before he was chosen to co-
OL,14,Fhost the top-rating Saturday night
OL,15,Fshow Game For A Laugh.
OL,17,FBut when Matthew first stepped foot in
OL,18,Fthe building he "felt fear".
