OL,7,F"Everything was so shiny and everyone
OL,8,Ffelt so important - and they were and
OL,9,FI wasn't," Matthew said.
OL,11,F"The thing I remember are the people.
OL,12,FThey were kind to me and funny and
OL,13,Fsupported me and were generous-
OL,14,Fspirited.
OL,16,F"I shall miss those people," he
OL,17,Fexplained.
OL,19,FThe site is being redeveloped as
OL,20,Foffices and workspaces for new media
OL,21,Fcompanies.
